						<div class="postbody">I don't know anything about MMC5, but can you use Mapper 4 (MMC3)?<br /><br />Use this <a href="http://pineight.com/nes/mapperwizard.html" class="postlink">Mapper Wizard</a> to find out if you can use it<br /><br />If you can use it then :<br />For making the hardware :<br />Prototype --&gt; <a href="http://nintendoallstars.w.interia.pl/romlab/mmc3_d.htm" class="postlink">Sacrifice a TxROM</a><br />mass produce --&gt; <a href="http://nintendoallstars.w.interia.pl/romlab/pmmc3.htm" class="postlink">use AX5202P which is a clone of MMC3</a><br /><br />Is your rom free to use? I would like to see it.</div>

					
